        "subject": "LU-1072 locking: bug in grouplock glimpse callback",
        "message": "LU-1072 locking: bug in grouplock glimpse callback\n\nWhen a file has more than 1 stripe, the grouplock glimpse\ncallback on mdt frees a grouplock temporary structure for each\nstripe.\nThe patch replace this structure by a global one associated to\nthe grouplock.\n\nChange-Id: Ifa1e93c928a74a7915a6b0eb5fdeecb9d0d74f39\nSigned-off-by: jcl <jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr>\n"
